{"tid":1091492,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"傳iPhone SE改名叫XE再度面世 OLED屏幕/平民價$4700","createTime":"2019-04-04T07:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T09:21:03.000Z","uid":212884,"like":21,"dislike":313,"uniUserReply":145,"replies":[{"pid":"34123a8e24097c1d6245e85780449a080d87bfb1","tid":1091492,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T07:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qhEi6uF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqhEi6uF.png&h=b8c13014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【iPhone傳聞】傳iPhone SE改名叫XE再度面世 OLED屏幕/平民價$4700<br />\n本地熱話科技<br />\n文: 杜比比鳥 15小時前<br />\n<br />\n之前就有傳聞指蘋果有機會在3月所舉行的蘋果發布會再度推出深受網民喜愛的iPhone SE 2，不過失望的是在Apple發布會2019中竟然沒有將iPhone SE 2發布，令一眾果粉大感失望。不過最近外國媒體iDropnews 就透露蘋果有機會將iPhone SE改革成iPhone XE系列再度推出市面，而規格上亦有所提升，一齊睇吓iPhone XE規格詳情。<br />\n根據外國媒體iDropnews透露，iPhone XE將會採用無邊框設計，而屏幕規格將會改為採用OLED屏幕，畫質更靚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SVjbG3e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSVjbG3e.png&h=e32a5fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niDropnews 透露iPhone XE的屏幕尺寸會比iPhone XS、 iPhone XS Max及 iPhone XR細，只有4.8吋，手細的朋友可以更易掌控。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LWYTaXc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLWYTaXc.png&h=f7e80e70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外亦與上一系列的iPhone SE一樣，採用長方型厚身設計，具年代感，而手機背面則採用鋁物料。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/463vXB8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F463vXB8.png&h=446a9c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手機同時亦會取消home鍵同新增Face ID功能。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9zOjQW2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9zOjQW2.png&h=da896e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外iDropnews表示，iPhone XE採用單鏡頭，相機規格有1200萬像素。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bSmp13D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbSmp13D.png&h=84554aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n價錢方面外國媒體普遍認為iPhone XE會繼續主打平民路線，預計售價大約為$600美元。（約$4,709港幣），如果iPhone SE真的改名再度回歸，一眾iPhone SE的忠粉們又有冇興趣買呢？<br />\n<br />\n資料及圖片來源：iDropnews <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/207230/iphone傳聞-傳iphone-se改名叫xe再度面世-oled屏幕-平民價-4700/2?utm_medium=share&amp;utm_source=clipboard_share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F207230%2Fiphone%E5%82%B3%E8%81%9E-%E5%82%B3iphone-se%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%ABxe%E5%86%8D%E5%BA%A6%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%96-oled%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95-%E5%B9%B3%E6%B0%91%E5%83%B9-4700%2F2%3Futm_medium%3Dshare%26utm_source%3Dclipboard_share&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvEtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=9b4b6b3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/207230/iphone傳聞-傳iphone-se改名叫xe再度面世-oled屏幕-平民價-4700/2?utm_medium=share&amp;utm_source=clipboard_share</a>"},{"pid":"8d60bec68f3e27624097f185e69c8754667fe6a3","tid":1091492,"uid":21886,"like":566,"dislike":0,"score":566,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T07:25:05.000Z","msg":"講撚到悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a20c9fe1b75b5ea54a93cfef367e864e97caea6","tid":1091492,"uid":5733,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T07:25:08.000Z","msg":"來啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0877a8f395ea20844be44f9b633cafef67575fc4","tid":1091492,"uid":14953,"like":105,"dislike":0,"score":105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T07:25:18.000Z","msg":"又打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4c5aa43d27878f85c1efbc762994235650cee3","tid":1091492,"uid":159313,"like":134,"dislike":1,"score":133,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"又撚班ifan<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93d6832afb96fa0d3b31f401dde0f7751b8f015","tid":1091492,"uid":212884,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime